They're a mostly Turkic Muslim group,

34
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:21,200
so the Party justifies it as a crackdown on
terrorists.

35
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,890
And it is true some Uighurs from Xinjiang

36
