about money.

70
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,670
Think about *that.*

71
00:02:48,670 --> 00:02:49,849
But the Muslim world’s silence

72
00:02:49,849 --> 00:02:52,060
on the Chinese regime’s persecution of Muslims

73
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:54,120
has started to change.

74
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,120
And it has started with

75
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:58,170
one of the most unlikely countries:

76
00:02:58,170 --> 00:02:59,180
Turkey.

77
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,180
Because when you think

78
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,870
‘standing up to authoritarian persecution,’

79
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:06,209
you think Turkish dictator President Erdoğan.

80
00:03:06,209 --> 00:03:09,020
Turkey has become the first predominantly
Muslim country

81
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:12,830
