96
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:54,620
“My name is Abdurehim Heyit.

97
00:03:54,629 --> 00:04:02,760
Today is February 10, 2019.

98
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,699
I'm in the process of being investigated

99
00:04:04,699 --> 00:04:11,819
for allegedly violating the national laws.

100
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:14,840
I'm now in good health and have never been
abused.”

101
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:20,700
Ohhh, well that was a bit of a snafu.

102
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:23,400
The Chinese Foreign Ministry was quick to
gloat.

103
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,980
“Turkey’s ridiculous lie of describing

104
00:04:25,980 --> 00:04:28,530
a person who is alive as a dead person

105
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:30,260
and its groundless accusations

106
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:33,000
